      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Jan 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://disorientcountry.club/announcements/2026-01-23-gate-hours/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Gate is not open 24 hours during the event. Please note the updated schedule:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Thursday&lt;/strong&gt;: Gates open Noon to 2AM&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Friday&lt;/strong&gt;: Gates open 9AM to 2AM&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Saturday&lt;/strong&gt;: Gates open 9AM to 10PM&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sunday&lt;/strong&gt;: Gate is closed to new arrivals&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;You will be allowed to go in and out once you have arrived, but please be respectful of the neighbors when you do so. Don&amp;rsquo;t be loud. No late night trips unless absolutely necessary.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
